<li><a href="http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/this-britain/hey-nonny-no-no-no-goths-and-pagans-are-reinventing-morris-dancing-823498.html" class="external text" title="http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/this-britain/hey-nonny-no-no-no-goths-and-pagans-are-reinventing-morris-dancing-823498.html" rel="nofollow">Goths and Pagans reinventing Morris Dancing</a> (<i><a href="/wiki/The_Independent" title="The Independent">The Independent</a></i> (UK), retrieved 11 May 2008)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/4123752/Morris-dancing-facing-extinction.html" class="external text" title="http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/4123752/Morris-dancing-facing-extinction.html" rel="nofollow">Morris dancing facing extinction</a> (<i><a href="/wiki/The_Daily_Telegraph" title="The Daily Telegraph">The Daily Telegraph</a></i> (UK),</li>
<li><a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1029342/" class="external text" title="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1029342/" rel="nofollow">Morris: A Life with Bells On IMDB article</a></li>
</ul>


